00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:16.900
Yeah.

00:16:16.900 --> 00:16:20.560
And there are a lot of nuances
on the hold out for sale.

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:22.000
The purpose of
going through this

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:24.291
